<FindBugsFilter xmlns="https://github.com/spotbugs/filter/3.0.0">
  <!--
    Reviewed suppressions (Chapter 16: suppress with a reason, never disable a whole detector).

    This module has NONE. The provider holds an immutable map of records and renders fresh strings on
    each call, the consumer holds only the contract value it expects, and the snapshot helper reads and
    writes files under the module's own test-resources tree — none of which trips a representation-
    exposure or resource detector. The filter is kept (empty) so a future, genuinely-reviewed
    suppression has a home with a written reason, rather than being added inline.
  -->
</FindBugsFilter>
